r2:AccomplishmentPlannedProgram.r2:Description:
The objectives of TMRR for the Mk21A RV program are as follows: 
1) to deliver preliminary designs to address evolving threats; 
2) incorporate a modular open systems architecture; 
3) perform cost capability analysis to aid with validation of user requirements; 
4) demonstrate performance of weapon system capabilities through prototyping, modeling, simulation, and testing.
